SECURITY
Domino's Pizza maintains
reasonable physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards to help guard your
information from loss, theft, misuse and unauthorized access, disclosure,
alteration, and destruction. Please be aware, however, that any email or other
transmission you send through the internet cannot be completely protected, and
we cannot guarantee the security of your information collected through our Web
Sites or Applications.
